  "format": "markdown",
  "sections": [
    {
      "heading": "标准巴什博弈",
      "level": 2,
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "<strong>规则描述</strong>：总共 <code>n</code> 个石子，两人轮流取，每次至少取 <code>1</code> 个，最多取 <code>m</code> 个，取走最后一个者胜。",
          "depth": 2
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "<strong>胜负判定核心结论</strong>：若 <code>n % (m + 1) == 0</code>，则后手必胜；否则先手必胜。",
          "depth": 2
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "heading": "扩展巴什博弈",
      "level": 2,
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "<strong>规则描述</strong>：总共 <code>n</code> 个石子，两人轮流取，每次至少取 <code>L</code> 个，最多取 <code>R</code> 个，取走最后一个者胜。",
          "depth": 2
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "<strong>胜负判定核心结论</strong>：关键在于计算 <code>n % (L + R)</code> 的余数 <code>remain</code>。",
          "depth": 2
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "1. 若 <code>remain == 0</code>，则后手必胜。",
          "depth": 2
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "2. 若 <code>1 &lt;= remain &lt;= L</code>，则后手必胜。",
          "depth": 2
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "3. 若 <code>L &lt; remain &lt;= R</code>，则先手必胜。",
          "depth": 2
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "4. 若 <code>R &lt; remain &lt; L + R</code>，则先手必胜。",
          "depth": 2
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
